strategy_rules: Prioritize micro-cap tokens (<100k) - they had the highest win rate among all market cap categories.
Avoid tokens with extreme volume spikes - trades with vol_extreme_spike averaged -23.4% ROI with 0% win rate.
Require age between 6-24h - trades in this age range had the highest win rate (46.2%) among all age categories.
Avoid tokens with high volume spikes - trades with vol_high_spike averaged -70.7% ROI with 0% win rate.
Favor tokens with moderate buy pressure - trades with pressure_strong_buying and pressure_heavy_buying had lower win rates than pressure_balanced.
Avoid mid-cap tokens (500k-2M) - they had a -71.6% average ROI with 0% win rate.
Prioritize tokens with buy ratio > 1.5 - winning trades had an average buy ratio of 1.93, while losing trades had an average buy ratio of 1.63.
avoid_conditions: AVOID tokens already pumped >100% in 1h (lost -29.8% on テディベア (TEDDY))
AVOID tokens with liq/MC ratio <5% (thin liquidity trap, lost on ORGAZM)
